1
00:00:00,480 --> 00:00:05,056
=Lost You Forever S1=

2
00:00:05,056 --> 00:00:07,296
(Lost You Forever S1 Special Edition 4)

3
00:00:09,560 --> 00:00:11,359
The nine-headed serpent demon
is Xiang Liu with Nine Lives.

4
00:00:11,399 --> 00:00:12,520
Rumor has it

5
00:00:12,560 --> 00:00:13,640
that he is crafty,

6
00:00:13,720 --> 00:00:15,279
with nine heads and nine lives.

7
00:00:15,319 --> 00:00:16,040
He is one

8
00:00:16,079 --> 00:00:17,559
of the most formidable figures
in Dahuang.

9
00:00:17,840 --> 00:00:19,520
Not only is
Xiang Liu's spirit power strong,

10
00:00:19,639 --> 00:00:20,840
but he is also brave and tactful,

11
00:00:21,120 --> 00:00:22,040
and knows military law

12
00:00:22,280 --> 00:00:23,159
and manages soldiers well.

13
00:00:23,600 --> 00:00:25,120
We can see how talented he is.

14
00:00:25,840 --> 00:00:26,639
Chubby,

15
00:00:27,000 --> 00:00:28,639
I told you several times.

16
00:00:28,799 --> 00:00:30,159
Humans are cunning.

17
00:00:30,280 --> 00:00:31,559
Have you learned a lesson this time?

18
00:00:35,080 --> 00:00:36,080
Please spare my life.

19
00:00:36,560 --> 00:00:37,119
Your Lordship.

20
00:00:37,279 --> 00:00:38,000
Antidote.

21
00:00:38,279 --> 00:00:39,159
I'll give you.

22
00:00:39,319 --> 00:00:41,040
I was just lucky.

23
00:00:41,159 --> 00:00:41,680
Your Lordship,

24
00:00:41,840 --> 00:00:43,639
I'm really a physician.

25
00:00:46,319 --> 00:00:47,000
Guards.

26
00:00:48,200 --> 00:00:48,959
Take him to the camp.

27
00:00:57,319 --> 00:00:58,319
(Xiang Liu with Nine Lives.)

28
00:00:59,599 --> 00:01:00,119
Who

29
00:01:00,119 --> 00:01:01,159
are you exactly?

30
00:01:01,279 --> 00:01:02,439
I am Wen Xiaoliu.

31
00:01:02,759 --> 00:01:03,919
But I don't believe it.

32
00:01:04,879 --> 00:01:06,319
I really am Wen Xiaoliu.

33
00:01:06,440 --> 00:01:07,440
If you want to live,

34
00:01:07,519 --> 00:01:08,360
then work for me.

35
00:01:08,480 --> 00:01:09,319
Be my man

36
00:01:09,559 --> 00:01:10,480
and obey me.

37
00:01:11,040 --> 00:01:12,239
I'll give you one night to consider.

38
00:01:12,680 --> 00:01:13,720
I want the answer tomorrow.

39
00:01:14,000 --> 00:01:15,040
I'm a bit thirsty.

40
00:01:15,639 --> 00:01:17,239
May I have some water first?

41
00:01:17,440 --> 00:01:18,080
Guards.

42
00:01:19,120 --> 00:01:19,919
Whip him.

43
00:01:22,144 --> 00:01:22,720
Your Lordship,

44
00:01:22,720 --> 00:01:23,760
20 lashes have been done.

45
00:01:23,919 --> 00:01:25,040
I still have one condition.

46
00:01:25,120 --> 00:01:25,639
Tell me.

47
00:01:25,639 --> 00:01:27,000
I will never leave Qingshui Town.

48
00:01:27,199 --> 00:01:27,744
Okay.

49
00:01:28,400 --> 00:01:30,239
Help me make the medicines I want.

50
00:01:30,360 --> 00:01:31,319
If you can't make it,

51
00:01:31,440 --> 00:01:32,680
then use your body in exchange.

52
00:01:32,760 --> 00:01:33,400
For the first time,

53
00:01:33,559 --> 00:01:35,160
let's start with your useless ears.

54
00:01:35,239 --> 00:01:36,279
After two times,

55
00:01:36,559 --> 00:01:37,480
let's go with the nose.

56
00:01:37,959 --> 00:01:39,080
I won't chop off your hands,

57
00:01:39,120 --> 00:01:40,440
because they are used to make medicine.

58
00:01:40,599 --> 00:01:41,639
I understand.

59
00:01:42,440 --> 00:01:43,519
You should know

60
00:01:43,839 --> 00:01:45,639
what kind of person I am.

61
00:01:46,120 --> 00:01:46,639
Your Lordship.

62
00:01:47,080 --> 00:01:48,040
Someone broke in.

63
00:01:48,680 --> 00:01:49,239
Your Lordship,

64
00:01:49,519 --> 00:01:50,839
I am already yours.

65
00:01:58,120 --> 00:01:59,120
Don't set your sights on him.

66
00:01:59,319 --> 00:02:00,400
He is mine now.

67
00:02:01,800 --> 00:02:02,559
Upon investigation,

68
00:02:02,919 --> 00:02:04,199
you're a civilian from Qingshui Town.

69
00:02:04,559 --> 00:02:05,480
You are free to go.

70
00:02:06,120 --> 00:02:06,919
(A woman)

71
00:02:07,080 --> 00:02:08,479
(is hiding her identity.)

72
00:02:09,919 --> 00:02:10,759
(Interesting.)

73
00:02:14,240 --> 00:02:15,960
Here comes an honored guest.

74
00:02:16,119 --> 00:02:16,800
This is a gift.

75
00:02:16,960 --> 00:02:17,960
You are a deity.

76
00:02:18,119 --> 00:02:19,520
When they all die,

77
00:02:19,559 --> 00:02:21,199
you might still be as you are now.

78
00:02:21,240 --> 00:02:22,000
Is it interesting?

79
00:02:22,320 --> 00:02:23,800
If I can't find enduring companionship,

80
00:02:23,919 --> 00:02:25,240
brief one is also good.

81
00:02:25,679 --> 00:02:26,960
Since you're here,

82
00:02:26,960 --> 00:02:28,360
have a drink before you leave.

83
00:02:28,679 --> 00:02:29,720
I brewed it.

84
00:02:29,960 --> 00:02:30,600
Have a try.

85
00:02:34,639 --> 00:02:36,080
Apart from the poison in the wine,

86
00:02:36,759 --> 00:02:38,000
there's nothing of value.

87
00:02:38,119 --> 00:02:39,240
So, have you been poisoned?

88
00:02:40,039 --> 00:02:41,199
Do you really want to poison me?

89
00:02:41,320 --> 00:02:43,440
For now, we're not enemies.

90
00:02:43,559 --> 00:02:45,160
I just want to beat you
with hundreds of whips.

91
00:02:45,160 --> 00:02:46,360
You wish.

92
00:02:53,639 --> 00:02:54,520
Can you swim?

93
00:02:54,639 --> 00:02:55,679
Want to have a competition?

94
00:02:55,839 --> 00:02:56,639
With you?

95
00:02:56,960 --> 00:02:57,720
You dare not?

96
00:02:57,919 --> 00:02:59,800
Since you're begging me,

97
00:03:00,479 --> 00:03:01,160
I agree.

98
00:03:01,839 --> 00:03:02,360
Let's start.

99
00:03:07,679 --> 00:03:08,399
You won.

100
00:03:08,559 --> 00:03:09,639
I'll grill a fish for you

101
00:03:09,720 --> 00:03:10,800
as a reward.

102
00:03:10,960 --> 00:03:12,160
I've always been curious.

103
00:03:12,160 --> 00:03:13,360
How did your nine heads

104
00:03:13,360 --> 00:03:14,119
grow?

105
00:03:14,119 --> 00:03:16,039
In a horizontal row?

106
00:03:16,039 --> 00:03:17,679
Or did they grow in a vertical row?

107
00:03:18,080 --> 00:03:19,080
Or from left to right?

108
00:03:19,240 --> 00:03:20,399
Don't your heads fight over food?

109
00:03:20,399 --> 00:03:21,880
Which one eats first?

110
00:03:21,920 --> 00:03:22,479
And the last...

111
00:03:27,440 --> 00:03:29,199
Actually, I prefer to eat mortals.

112
00:03:29,360 --> 00:03:30,720
Someone like you is just enough

113
00:03:30,800 --> 00:03:33,399
for each of my heads to take a bite.

114
00:03:36,039 --> 00:03:37,440
You have little spirit power,

115
00:03:37,720 --> 00:03:39,240
but your body is a treasure.

116
00:03:39,520 --> 00:03:40,119
You really

117
00:03:40,440 --> 00:03:41,440
eat people?

118
00:03:41,960 --> 00:03:43,160
Dare to talk nonsense now?

119
00:03:43,200 --> 00:03:43,712
No,

120
00:03:44,064 --> 00:03:44,608
no.

121
00:03:51,960 --> 00:03:52,839
Who sent you?

122
00:03:53,039 --> 00:03:54,320
This is far from the camp.

123
00:03:54,360 --> 00:03:55,720
You shouldn't be here.

124
00:03:55,960 --> 00:03:56,479
I'm here

125
00:03:56,520 --> 00:03:58,240
on the orders of General Hong Jiang

126
00:03:58,479 --> 00:03:59,639
to inspect this area.

127
00:04:01,279 --> 00:04:02,080
You may leave.

128
00:04:02,199 --> 00:04:03,000
I shall take my leave.

129
00:04:06,440 --> 00:04:08,039
The secret report said
you wanted to see me.

130
00:04:08,639 --> 00:04:09,679
What exactly is so urgent?

131
00:04:11,279 --> 00:04:12,160
Xiang Liu.

132
00:04:14,039 --> 00:04:14,960
Are you looking for him?

133
00:05:01,519 --> 00:05:02,720
Who sent you?

134
00:05:24,000 --> 00:05:24,799
Catch him alive.

135
00:06:01,559 --> 00:06:02,359
Don't hit my face.

136
00:06:15,959 --> 00:06:17,239
You're sleeping on my bed.

137
00:06:17,399 --> 00:06:18,279
Where should I sleep?

138
00:06:18,528 --> 00:06:19,079
Nine-headed demon.

139
00:06:20,359 --> 00:06:20,920
Nine-headed demon.

140
00:06:22,239 --> 00:06:23,559
When healing your wounds,

141
00:06:23,559 --> 00:06:25,160
you can't lose focus.

142
00:06:25,279 --> 00:06:26,119
How the tables

143
00:06:26,119 --> 00:06:27,559
have turned on you!

144
00:06:28,160 --> 00:06:29,480
Focus on healing.

145
00:06:29,519 --> 00:06:31,200
Don't be disturbed by me.

146
00:06:32,920 --> 00:06:34,000
These two strands of hair.

147
00:06:36,359 --> 00:06:37,079
Let me show you.

148
00:06:39,359 --> 00:06:41,839
I will eat you.

149
00:06:42,160 --> 00:06:43,279
Come on. There you go.

150
00:06:44,359 --> 00:06:45,640
Looks like you're almost done.

151
00:06:45,640 --> 00:06:46,600
Then I'll leave now.

152
00:06:46,720 --> 00:06:47,959
I will disappear for a few days.

153
00:06:48,000 --> 00:06:49,399
When you start
to appreciate my goodness,

154
00:06:49,640 --> 00:06:50,239
I'll come back.

155
00:06:56,519 --> 00:06:57,839
Want to eat me?

156
00:06:58,040 --> 00:06:59,119
Come on. There you go.

157
00:06:59,119 --> 00:07:00,160
Wen Xiaoliu,

158
00:07:00,359 --> 00:07:02,160
we'll settle this account slowly.

159
00:07:02,640 --> 00:07:04,119
We have all the time in the world.

160
00:07:09,760 --> 00:07:11,399
He actually dares to come to me.

161
00:07:12,480 --> 00:07:13,880
Is he planning to repay me?

162
00:07:15,839 --> 00:07:16,920
I'll give you three choices.

163
00:07:16,992 --> 00:07:17,559
First,

164
00:07:17,640 --> 00:07:18,679
whip me 40 times.

165
00:07:18,944 --> 00:07:19,480
Second,

166
00:07:19,760 --> 00:07:20,799
kick me out of here.

167
00:07:20,992 --> 00:07:21,559
Third,

168
00:07:21,600 --> 00:07:22,559
listen to my serious matter.

169
00:07:22,679 --> 00:07:23,440
A serious matter.

170
00:07:30,399 --> 00:07:31,880
Why are you taking so much?

171
00:07:31,880 --> 00:07:33,640
I only know you have nine heads,

172
00:07:34,040 --> 00:07:35,399
but I don't know you have nine stomachs.

173
00:07:35,760 --> 00:07:36,519
Tell me

174
00:07:36,920 --> 00:07:37,959
when I should

175
00:07:38,160 --> 00:07:39,679
bite this off?

176
00:07:39,760 --> 00:07:41,200
Such a beautiful night.

177
00:07:41,600 --> 00:07:42,399
How elegant it is

178
00:07:42,399 --> 00:07:43,359
to talk under the moon.

179
00:07:43,880 --> 00:07:44,679
Don't you hate me?

180
00:07:45,079 --> 00:07:46,200
I don't hate you.

181
00:07:46,600 --> 00:07:47,320
I really don't.

182
00:07:47,519 --> 00:07:48,160
Because...

183
00:07:48,480 --> 00:07:49,200
I'm lonely.

184
00:07:49,720 --> 00:07:50,920
I had a strange disease before,

185
00:07:51,079 --> 00:07:52,399
so I hid in the deep mountain.

186
00:07:52,640 --> 00:07:54,279
Then I met a snake demon.

187
00:07:54,440 --> 00:07:55,880
But even knowing the danger,

188
00:07:56,239 --> 00:07:57,440
I still provoked it all the time.

189
00:07:57,559 --> 00:07:58,440
Because only it could

190
00:07:58,640 --> 00:07:59,799
understand what I was saying.

191
00:08:01,640 --> 00:08:02,839
That snake later...

192
00:08:04,000 --> 00:08:04,600
Died.

193
00:08:04,799 --> 00:08:05,480
You killed it?

194
00:08:05,559 --> 00:08:06,200
A nine-tailed fox.

195
00:08:06,519 --> 00:08:07,399
What about the fox?

196
00:08:07,679 --> 00:08:09,160
He locked me in a cage

197
00:08:09,600 --> 00:08:11,079
and forced me to eat disgusting things

198
00:08:11,239 --> 00:08:12,320
because he wanted to fatten me

199
00:08:12,399 --> 00:08:13,040
before eating me.

200
00:08:13,320 --> 00:08:14,239
You mean

201
00:08:14,359 --> 00:08:15,679
I'm just like that snake.

202
00:08:16,920 --> 00:08:18,559
We're both things for you
to alleviate loneliness.

203
00:08:18,720 --> 00:08:19,920
Perhaps, to you,

204
00:08:19,920 --> 00:08:21,640
I am the snake that amuses you.

205
00:08:22,160 --> 00:08:23,640
Didn't you come to me for business?

206
00:08:23,839 --> 00:08:24,720
I don't need your help.

207
00:08:24,959 --> 00:08:25,799
I'll ask someone else.

208
00:08:32,520 --> 00:08:33,056
You,

209
00:08:33,479 --> 00:08:34,719
at most,

210
00:08:34,719 --> 00:08:36,200
are that snake egg eaten by others.

211
00:08:43,599 --> 00:08:44,640
Patrolling around

212
00:08:44,799 --> 00:08:45,880
in the middle of the night.

213
00:08:46,159 --> 00:08:47,719
I think the most likely to betray us

214
00:08:47,760 --> 00:08:48,679
is that nine-headed demon.

215
00:08:48,880 --> 00:08:50,000
General trusts

216
00:08:50,000 --> 00:08:51,200
that lowly creature so much.

217
00:08:51,400 --> 00:08:53,080
It really is unsettling.

218
00:08:57,952 --> 00:08:58,520
Come here.

219
00:08:58,880 --> 00:08:59,679
He's not going anywhere.

220
00:08:59,799 --> 00:09:00,599
Say what you want

221
00:09:00,599 --> 00:09:01,359
right here.

222
00:09:03,080 --> 00:09:04,239
Are you coming over by yourself,

223
00:09:04,479 --> 00:09:05,679
or you want me to come to you?

224
00:09:06,520 --> 00:09:07,039
Get on.

225
00:09:07,400 --> 00:09:07,936
I'm coming.

226
00:09:13,039 --> 00:09:13,880
Chubby!

227
00:09:14,599 --> 00:09:16,320
Chubby, you crazy bird,

228
00:09:16,400 --> 00:09:17,520
stop it.

229
00:09:17,520 --> 00:09:18,479
Chubby!

230
00:09:24,159 --> 00:09:25,400
Are you in a bad mood today?

231
00:09:25,559 --> 00:09:26,840
Whenever you're upset,

232
00:09:27,159 --> 00:09:28,239
you would torment me for fun.

233
00:09:30,679 --> 00:09:32,200
Why is your spirit power so low?

234
00:09:32,400 --> 00:09:33,760
It's all because of that stupid fox.

235
00:09:34,280 --> 00:09:35,760
In case my spirit power

236
00:09:35,799 --> 00:09:36,400
didn't go in vain,

237
00:09:36,520 --> 00:09:37,679
he used medicine to disable me.

238
00:09:37,919 --> 00:09:39,200
I heard the pain

239
00:09:39,559 --> 00:09:40,880
is like bones being drilled.

240
00:09:41,039 --> 00:09:42,119
It seems that my 40 lashes

241
00:09:42,119 --> 00:09:42,919
were too light for you.

242
00:09:43,280 --> 00:09:44,520
It's precisely because I suffered

243
00:09:44,719 --> 00:09:45,679
so much back then

244
00:09:46,119 --> 00:09:47,440
that I'm really afraid of pain now.

245
00:09:47,599 --> 00:09:48,359
In the end,

246
00:09:48,359 --> 00:09:49,799
I stayed silent and uncooperative,

247
00:09:49,919 --> 00:09:50,599
even trying to die.

248
00:09:52,080 --> 00:09:53,840
Even someone like you would seek death?

249
00:09:54,159 --> 00:09:55,479
But I never managed to die.

250
00:10:01,754 --> 00:10:05,408
♪Seaside moonlight shines on my clothes♪

251
00:10:05,408 --> 00:10:08,538
♪Clothing as white as snow♪

252
00:10:09,088 --> 00:10:12,858
♪You laugh♪

253
00:10:12,960 --> 00:10:16,160
♪Eyes like stars♪

254
00:10:16,544 --> 00:10:19,280
♪Immersed in longing♪

255
00:10:19,280 --> 00:10:20,760
You look quite different

256
00:10:20,919 --> 00:10:21,840
tonight.

257
00:10:23,000 --> 00:10:24,679
Did something unpleasant happen?

258
00:10:24,679 --> 00:10:26,080
♪Carved in my bones and heart♪

259
00:10:26,080 --> 00:10:27,919
You lived by the water
when you were a child?

260
00:10:31,817 --> 00:10:35,008
♪Waiting for snow♪

261
00:10:35,642 --> 00:10:38,778
♪Waiting for destiny's favor♪

262
00:10:39,328 --> 00:10:45,696
♪Waiting for you a lifetime♪

263
00:10:46,938 --> 00:10:49,952
♪Yearning surpasses time♪

264
00:10:50,592 --> 00:10:53,818
♪Waiting brings no bloom♪

265
00:10:54,320 --> 00:10:56,400
Life is precious as long as we can

266
00:10:57,520 --> 00:10:58,679
enjoy such views.

267
00:11:00,000 --> 00:11:01,159
Sceneries are dead.

268
00:11:01,799 --> 00:11:02,440
It's meanings

269
00:11:03,080 --> 00:11:04,400
from people that make them alive.

270
00:11:05,402 --> 00:11:09,056
♪It's longing. It's self-pity♪

271
00:11:09,177 --> 00:11:12,693
♪The tones of tenderness♪

272
00:11:12,864 --> 00:11:16,922
♪It's muteness. It's imprisonment♪

273
00:11:16,922 --> 00:11:20,192
♪Scenes unfurl within myself♪

274
00:11:20,493 --> 00:11:24,224
♪It's the way back. It's the way home♪

275
00:11:24,608 --> 00:11:27,936
♪Life is like dancing in the snow♪

276
00:11:27,936 --> 00:11:30,682
♪It's loneliness♪

277
00:11:32,640 --> 00:11:33,919
Why are you in a bad mood?

278
00:11:34,159 --> 00:11:35,479
The trend of the world is irreversible.

279
00:11:35,640 --> 00:11:37,320
It's not something
an individual can stop.

280
00:11:37,479 --> 00:11:38,359
In your view,

281
00:11:39,559 --> 00:11:40,520
what should I do?

282
00:11:40,520 --> 00:11:42,440
If you like power,

283
00:11:42,479 --> 00:11:43,640
you can defect from Hong Jiang

284
00:11:43,760 --> 00:11:44,880
to the King of Xiyan.

285
00:11:50,359 --> 00:11:51,280
I was wrong.

286
00:11:51,440 --> 00:11:52,119
I was wrong.

287
00:12:01,520 --> 00:12:02,039
Mr. Xiang,

288
00:12:02,239 --> 00:12:03,000
recently in the camp,

289
00:12:03,080 --> 00:12:04,280
many people got sick

290
00:12:04,719 --> 00:12:05,239
from malaria.

291
00:12:06,119 --> 00:12:07,559
