call you a nine-headed monster?

579
00:25:04,160 --> 00:25:05,119
What I hate

580
00:25:06,280 --> 00:25:07,959
is not them talking about me
being a monster,

581
00:25:08,040 --> 00:25:09,640
but their underlying contempt

582
00:25:10,079 --> 00:25:10,760
and disdain.

583
00:25:11,000 --> 00:25:11,800
I allow you to do it

584
00:25:12,599 --> 00:25:13,199
because...

585
00:25:18,400 --> 00:25:20,160
Because you make fun in your mouth,

586
00:25:21,160 --> 00:25:21,959
but in your heart,

587
00:25:24,119 --> 00:25:25,920
you never thought
that a nine-headed demon is weird.

588
00:25:26,400 --> 00:25:27,800
I used to be weirder than you.

589
00:25:28,079 --> 00:25:29,359
So you hid in the deep mountains,

590
00:25:30,319 --> 00:25:31,079
and didn't see anyone?

591
00:25:36,479 --> 00:25:38,319
Are we having a heart-to-heart talk
under the moon,

592
00:25:39,280 --> 00:25:40,280
trying to get along?

593
00:25:42,319 --> 00:25:43,959
Before you irritate me again,

594
00:25:44,480 --> 00:25:45,079
I suppose so.

595
00:25:45,479 --> 00:25:46,199
What a pity.

596
00:25:46,520 --> 00:25:48,280
Harmonious moments are always short.

597
00:25:48,560 --> 00:25:49,640
Beautiful things

598
00:25:50,439 --> 00:25:51,640
never last long.

599
00:25:56,160 --> 00:25:57,680
I heard Xuan got better.

600
00:25:57,880 --> 00:26:00,000
Did you save him?

601
00:26:01,000 --> 00:26:02,199
He was in danger twice.

602
00:26:02,359 --> 00:26:03,160
You saved him twice.

603
00:26:03,800 --> 00:26:05,199
Anything is bothering you?

604
00:26:05,520 --> 00:26:06,319
I was thinking

605
00:26:06,479 --> 00:26:07,839
about how to remove the poisonous bug

606
00:26:07,959 --> 00:26:09,000
from Xuan.

607
00:26:09,160 --> 00:26:09,920
Find another person

608
00:26:10,640 --> 00:26:11,800
and lure the bug into him.

609
00:26:12,400 --> 00:26:13,959
Not anyone can do it.

610
00:26:13,959 --> 00:26:14,520
Why?

611
00:26:14,560 --> 00:26:15,599
You raised the poisonous bug.

612
00:26:16,199 --> 00:26:17,199
You don't know why?

613
00:26:17,280 --> 00:26:18,319
Many years ago,

614
00:26:18,319 --> 00:26:19,599
I met

615
00:26:19,599 --> 00:26:20,800
a dying old woman.

616
00:26:20,800 --> 00:26:22,119
I gave her a bath.

617
00:26:22,199 --> 00:26:23,920
I cleaned her up nicely

618
00:26:23,920 --> 00:26:25,719
and sent her to meet her lover.

619
00:26:25,839 --> 00:26:26,520
She gave me

620
00:26:26,520 --> 00:26:28,359
a walnut as a reward,

621
00:26:28,400 --> 00:26:30,079
and inside it was a pair
of poisonous bugs.

622
00:26:30,079 --> 00:26:31,119
Nonsense.

623
00:26:31,239 --> 00:26:32,920
The only way to remove the poisonous bug

624
00:26:32,920 --> 00:26:33,800
from Xuan is

625
00:26:33,800 --> 00:26:35,520
to lure it into another person.

626
00:26:35,800 --> 00:26:36,760
Mostly,

627
00:26:36,800 --> 00:26:38,239
women raise it

628
00:26:38,239 --> 00:26:39,319
for their lovers.

629
00:26:39,599 --> 00:26:40,560
Once planted,

630
00:26:41,119 --> 00:26:42,479
the couple will live

631
00:26:42,479 --> 00:26:43,719
and die together.

632
00:26:43,839 --> 00:26:45,119
Will it work if there's no love

633
00:26:45,239 --> 00:26:45,880
between the couple?

634
00:26:45,920 --> 00:26:47,199
No, no, no.

635
00:26:47,479 --> 00:26:48,839
(Even so,)

636
00:26:49,000 --> 00:26:50,400
(there would be endless trouble.)

637
00:26:50,599 --> 00:26:51,920
(Once you give your heart,)

638
00:26:52,119 --> 00:26:54,319
(you can never take it back.)

639
00:26:54,680 --> 00:26:55,880
You're a nine-headed demon.

640
00:26:56,079 --> 00:26:57,760
Can you do me a favor

641
00:26:57,839 --> 00:26:59,880
and lure the poisonous bug into you?

642
00:27:00,199 --> 00:27:02,040
I can help you,

643
00:27:02,119 --> 00:27:02,959
but you have to promise

644
00:27:03,199 --> 00:27:04,719
you'll help me
with one thing in the future.

645
00:27:05,000 --> 00:27:05,920
As soon as I say it,

646
00:27:06,119 --> 00:27:06,880
you can't refuse.

647
00:27:07,616 --> 00:27:08,199
Deal.

648
00:27:09,280 --> 00:27:10,280
If you break the oath,

649
00:27:10,319 --> 00:27:11,319
all your pleasures

650
00:27:12,599 --> 00:27:13,479
will turn into pain,

651
00:27:15,199 --> 00:27:16,119
and all your happiness

652
00:27:17,719 --> 00:27:18,599
will turn into sorrow.

653
00:27:19,560 --> 00:27:20,719
If I lure the poisonous bug out,

654
00:27:20,880 --> 00:27:22,119
right now,

655
00:27:22,359 --> 00:27:23,400
you're a bit too far away.

656
00:27:23,400 --> 00:27:24,280
We need to go

657
00:27:24,280 --> 00:27:25,479
to the Wushen Mountain in Haoling.

658
00:27:25,760 --> 00:27:27,920
The Wushen Mountain
is where King of Haoling resides.

659
00:27:28,079 --> 00:27:29,040
It's heavily guarded.

660
00:27:29,439 --> 00:27:30,599
We'll go by sea.

661
00:27:30,680 --> 00:27:32,800
I guess we could avoid the guards.

662
00:27:37,959 --> 00:27:40,000
We've reached the sea area
of Wushen Mountain.

663
00:27:40,680 --> 00:27:41,800
You can try to lure the bug out.

664
00:27:42,272 --> 00:27:47,119
♪I pray for having you♪

665
00:27:47,119 --> 00:27:48,119
You apply to the other half.

666
00:27:48,920 --> 00:27:50,719
(The love poisonous bug)

667
00:27:51,199 --> 00:27:52,160
(not only wants your life)

668
00:27:53,040 --> 00:27:54,000
(but also your heart.)

669
00:27:54,239 --> 00:27:55,599
(Once you give your heart,)

670
00:27:55,719 --> 00:27:58,000
(you can never take it back.)

671
00:27:59,008 --> 00:28:03,680
♪Walking in the mortal with you♪

672
00:28:03,680 --> 00:28:04,439
I think this bug

673
00:28:04,439 --> 00:28:05,880
isn't as simple as I thought.

674
00:28:05,920 --> 00:28:06,719
I thought

675
00:28:07,880 --> 00:28:08,760
we should run.

676
00:28:10,784 --> 00:28:15,119
♪For our permanent love to continue♪

677
00:28:15,119 --> 00:28:16,199
So many seaweeds.

678
00:28:16,560 --> 00:28:17,560
They're endless.

679
00:28:18,079 --> 00:28:19,359
Look at the jellyfish.

680
00:28:19,680 --> 00:28:21,040
I can make them into beautiful lamps.

681
00:28:21,984 --> 00:28:22,520
Right?

682
00:28:22,520 --> 00:28:28,282
♪I'll hold you till the end of the world♪

683
00:28:28,992 --> 00:28:33,466
♪That's our destiny♪

684
00:28:34,106 --> 00:28:39,648
♪I almost forgot about
the first time I met you♪

685
00:28:40,736 --> 00:28:45,664
♪The destiny brought us together♪

686
00:28:45,888 --> 00:28:51,666
♪We drank and sang under the moon♪

687
00:28:51,776 --> 00:28:55,296
♪My heart is empty♪

688
00:28:55,296 --> 00:28:57,344
♪A new moon sets♪

689
00:28:57,626 --> 00:28:59,552
♪Joys and sorrows are mixed♪

690
00:28:59,776 --> 00:29:03,168
♪The wind and rain beat down on me♪

691
00:29:03,456 --> 00:29:07,002
♪My eyes are wet♪

692
00:29:07,104 --> 00:29:09,466
♪The view is splendid♪

693
00:29:09,632 --> 00:29:11,578
♪With blooming flowers♪

694
00:29:11,578 --> 00:29:15,072
♪But I prefer the worldly life♪
